 we show that weakly interacting massive particles (WIMPs) as\ndark matter annihilate efficiently inside UCMHs to yield cosmic rays far\nexceeding the observed flux. Our bound gives severe restriction on the\ncompatibility between the particle physics models for WIMPs and the PBH\nscenario as the explanation of MBHs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 May 2014 09:29:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Oct 2014 06:17:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-17"}
