ollisions may also lead to the formation of G2-like cloud-like\nobjects such as the one recently observed in the Galactic center.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 May 2014 11:42:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Nov 2014 04:02:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
